Approach 2: 

A Binary number will only have one 1 
eg: 16-> 10000 -> binary
eg: 5 ->   101 -> Not binary
we loop through and get remainder and if its ==1 then its Binary else not binart 


if n<=0: return False
result=0
while n!=0:
  rem= n%2
  result+= rem
  n=n//2

return result==1
